content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 143.3 - Movement of regulated articles within the quarantine area

State Regulations
A regulated article may be moved freely within the
quarantine area, provided the regulated article is otherwise eligible for
unrestricted movement under all other state and federal plant quarantines and
regulations applicable to the regulated article. Notes
